                        <lb n="2"/><seg met="–⏕–⏕–"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></seg> <supplied reason="lost">ἐν συ</supplied>νόδοις ὀλόμαν
                        <lb n="3"/><seg met="–⏕–⏕–"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></seg> <rs type="institution" subtype="social_group" role="belonging" key="koinonE" ref="#oreioi"><w lemma="πατρίς"><supplied reason="lost">πατ</supplied>ρὶ<unclear>ς</unclear></w></rs> δέ μοί ἐστιν <placeName ref="#oreioi" type="ethnic">Ὀρειοί</placeName>
                        <lb n="4"/><seg met="–⏕–⏕–"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></seg> <supplied reason="lost">τοῖς ἐπ</supplied>ιγινομένοις <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.
                </ab>
